description:
In this course titled 'Psychic Powers – Create Psychic Shield For Protection' By Pradeep Aggarwal , you will learn -

Psychic shield is the method to defending against negative energies and psychic attacks. Psychic shield is a protective shield around yourself to protect both your physical and mental body.

This course is designed to help you create your own psychic shields to protect yourself from the negative energies around you.

It is ideal for people who are into sports and the corporate world , who have lots of people around them who spread negativity by passing negative comments and demotivating others.

By the end of the course you will be more positive and feel more protective by not letting your energies drain by people's comments and thoughts . You will perform at your best and feel motivated all the time.

You will also learn more about conscious and sub conscious mind and instant relaxation using self hypnosis.

You will overcome all the myths about self hypnosis and have a strong positive mind.

This course contains a lot of psychic exercises and more than 35 minutes of live video content designed over 7 lectures in English including a bonus e-book on positive affirmations.
title: Psychic Powers – Create Psychic Shield For Protection
